# CLAUDE.local.md - Personal Overrides (DO NOT COMMIT)

Rename this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` (without `.example`) for personal overrides. It is gitignored.

Use this file for:

- your preferred coding style details that differ from team conventions
- personal model defaults (e.g. "I always want Opus for debugging")
- short-term reminders scoped to your current context window
- local credentials notes (never the credentials themselves)

Do NOT put in here:

- actual secrets, API keys, tokens
- anything the rest of the team also needs (that goes in AGENTS.md)

## Example sections

### My preferred defaults

- Default Claude model: Claude Sonnet 4.6
- Take checkpoint every 3 file edits.
- Prefer named functions over arrow functions in TS.

